feedback_text: The sound quality of the speakers is excellent, but connectivity drops intermittently.
I loved the modern design of the lamp, although it feels a bit too fragile.
The fabric is soft and comfortable, but the stitching could be improved.
Battery life exceeded expectations, lasting almost two days on a single charge.
The packaging was messy, and the product tasted slightly stale.
agent_notes: Urgent quality check and supplier review needed.

feedback_text: The jacket is stylish but seems to run small compared to standard sizes.
agent_notes: Check sizing guidelines and feedback consistency.

feedback_text: The furniture has a modern look, yet the assembly instructions were confusing and incomplete.
agent_notes: Revise the user manual for clarity.

feedback_text: The laptop offers great performance for the price, though it tends to overheat during extended use.
The dessert was delightful in taste, but the presentation left much to be desired.
agent_notes: Explore ways to improve visual appeal.

feedback_text: The smart thermostat is user-friendly and energy-efficient; however, the mobile app interface could be more intuitive.
agent_notes: Forward feedback for app interface redesign.

feedback_text: The running shoes are lightweight and comfortable, but the soles wear out too quickly.
